<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>赏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柳下湖波里，轻舟独自横。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛羊行陌野，嚼草露晶晶。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/cddfec27f3fa4a52909918bbf79162b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
